</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_231" id="114r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l14"><expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan> Höfner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l16"> <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkhart / . VVir danken ew cʒemal fleiʒʒıklich / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒü </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l15">bey </ab></add> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l17"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tag cʒü <expan>Alerſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein vvolt / vnd als derſelb tag <expan>erleng<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l18">vnd Caſpar <expan>Sweppf<ex>er</ex>man</expan> einen <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tag <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſol / aber gen <expan>Alerſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l19"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr auf <expan>de<ex>n</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag vvenn Jn <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Sweppf<ex>er</ex>man</expan> ſecʒe / bey den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü <expan>Alerſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ſein wöllet / Vnd habt die müwe <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_231_r3l21">Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_231_r3l22">Hanſen <expan>Strüpperg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſi<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_231" id="114r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan> Höfner</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkhart, wir danken ew czemal fleizziklich,
                        daz ir <add>bey</add> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tag czü
                            <expan>Alersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sein wolt und als derselb tag
                                <expan>erleng<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und Caspar
                            <expan>Sweppf<ex>er</ex>man</expan> einen <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        tag <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> sol aber gen
                            <expan>Alersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir auf <expan>de<ex>n</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag, wenn in
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Sweppf<ex>er</ex>man</expan> secze, bey den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü <expan>Alersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                        sein wöllet und habt die müwe <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Hansen <expan>Strüpperg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
